{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-all-timeline-js","path":"/2019/11/22/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"allAwesomeItem":{"nodes":[{"awesomeListRepo":"caufieldjh/awesome-bioie","categoryHTML":"<h2>Groups Active in the Field</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.brown.edu/academics/medical/about-us/research/centers-institutes-and-programs/biomedical-informatics/\">Brown Center for Biomedical Informatics</a> - Based at Brown University and directed by Dr. Neil Sarkar, whose research group works on topics in clinical NLP and IE.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-11-22T21:07:53.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"caufieldjh/awesome-bioie","categoryHTML":"<h2>Groups Active in the Field</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://compbio.ucdenver.edu/Hunter_lab/CCP_website/index.html\">Center for Computational Pharmacology NLP Group</a> - based at University of Colorado, Denver and led by Larry Hunter - <a href=\"https://github.com/UCDenver-ccp\">see their GitHub repos here.</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-11-22T21:07:53.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"caufieldjh/awesome-bioie","categoryHTML":"<h2>Groups Active in the Field</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://jensenlab.org/\">JensenLab</a> - Based at the Novo Nordisk Foundation Center for Protein Research at the University of Copenhagen, Denmark.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-11-22T21:07:53.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"caufieldjh/awesome-bioie","categoryHTML":"<h2>Groups Active in the Field</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.nactem.ac.uk/\">National Centre for Text Mining (NaCTeM)</a> - Based at the University of Manchester and led by Prof. Sophia Ananiadou, NaCTeM is concerned with text mining in general but has a particular focus on biomedical applications.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-11-22T21:07:53.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"caufieldjh/awesome-bioie","categoryHTML":"<h2>Groups Active in the Field</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.mayo.edu/research/departments-divisions/department-health-sciences-research/medical-informatics/projects\">Mayo Clinic's clinical natural language processing program</a> - Several groups at Mayo Clinic have made major contributions to BioIE (for example, the Apache cTAKES platform) over the past 20 years.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-11-22T21:07:53.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"caufieldjh/awesome-bioie","categoryHTML":"<h2>Groups Active in the Field</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://monarchinitiative.org/\">Monarch Initiative</a> - A joint effort between groups at Oregon State University, Oregon Health &#x26; Science University, Lawrence Berkeley National Lab, The Jackson Laboratory, and several others, seeking to \"integrate biological information using semantics, and present it in a novel way, leveraging phenotypes to bridge the knowledge gap\".</li>","updatedAt":"2019-11-22T21:07:53.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"caufieldjh/awesome-bioie","categoryHTML":"<h2>Groups Active in the Field</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://turkunlp.org/\">TurkuNLP</a> - Based at the University of Turku and concerned with NLP in general with a focus on BioNLP and clinical applications.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-11-22T21:07:53.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"caufieldjh/awesome-bioie","categoryHTML":"<h2>Groups Active in the Field</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://sbmi.uth.edu/nlp/\">UTHealth Houston Biomedical Natural Language Processing Lab</a> - Based in the University of Texas Health Science Center at Houston, School of Biomedical Informatics and led by Dr. Hua Xu.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-11-22T21:07:53.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"caufieldjh/awesome-bioie","categoryHTML":"<h2>Groups Active in the Field</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://nlp.cs.vcu.edu/\">VCU Natural Language Processing Lab</a> - Based at Virginia Commonwealth University and led by Dr. Bridget McInnes.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-11-22T21:07:53.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"caufieldjh/awesome-bioie","categoryHTML":"<h2>Groups Active in the Field</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://zaklab.org\">Zaklab</a> - Group led by Dr. Isaac Kohane at Harvard Medical School's Department of Biomedical Informatics (Dr. Kohane is also a steward of the n2c2 (formerly i2b2) datasets - see <a href=\"#datasets\">Datasets</a> below).</li>","updatedAt":"2019-11-22T21:07:53.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"caufieldjh/awesome-bioie","categoryHTML":"<h2>Groups Active in the Field</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.dbmi.columbia.edu/\">Columbia University Department of Biomedical Informatics</a> - Led by Drs. George Hripcsak and Noémie Elhadad.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-11-22T21:07:53.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"caufieldjh/awesome-bioie","categoryHTML":"<h2>Research Overviews</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6250990/\">Capturing the Patient's Perspective: a Review of Advances in Natural Language Processing of Health-Related Text</a> - A 2017 review of natural language processing methods applied to information extraction in health records and social media text. An important note from this review: \"One of the main challenges in the field is the availability of data that can be shared and which can be used by the community to push the development of methods based on comparable and reproducible studies\".</li>","updatedAt":"2019-11-22T20:55:40.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"frenck/awesome-home-assistant","categoryHTML":"<h2>Dashboards</h2><h3>Custom Cards</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/bokub/rgb-light-card\">RGB Light Card</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/bokub/rgb-light-card\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;backgrou